元資產投資者的信心 :<span style=\"color: red;\">「金融市場互相聯繫，美國嘅金融機構、投資基金喺呢度有咁嘅利益，如果我哋呢度（香港）打個乞嗤，對佢哋都會有影響」</span>...<br />\n<br />\n....「我哋個聯繫匯率1983年實施，美國政策法裏面話俾香港特殊待遇嗰條例就1992年，你由呢個時序就理解到，我哋實施聯繫匯率係唔使佢同意，係我哋自設嘅制度。」<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200613/UZWWOSILKZLJOZJJUMTTVMFA6U/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200613%2FUZWWOSILKZLJOZJJUMTTVMFA6U%2F&d=9%2FF7mzj%2FI7OrL%2BCOzrVJrgy1DEY80m5I9K8mtjxpzv8%3D&h=14587dd2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200613%2FUZWWOSILKZLJOZJJUMTTVMFA6U%2F&h=ea5abbc2\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200613/UZWWOSILKZLJOZJJUMTTVMFA6U/</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-13T07:19:18.000Z","msg":"驚你傳染啲病菌比佢咋"},{"pid":"d765cad543ba42264567c888f57ce06ead2632aa","tid":2062420,"uid":108078,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-13T07:21:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />港幣幾時做第一貨幣"},{"pid":"2133ef0d0fc54cddb88bf6e4fa5289d7e1f59aa2","tid":2062420,"uid":154429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-13T07:22:30.000Z","msg":"成班官都on9 , 唔比美元你點玩呀？"},{"pid":"77950c939a5f0c5b456e3d868f3c7a3c59d85aa8","tid":2062420,"uid":522,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"7d45fe8342284c47357f5c78372d46e1d10f9893","tid":2062420,"uid":262423,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-13T07:17:11.000Z","msg":"原來全世界都睇香港頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-13T07:24:54.000Z","msg":"所以美國佬會拎返走香港金融國際中心既地位"},{"pid":"8ba11a283440955fa6c0e84c54de576d83e8f186","tid":2062420,"uid":249526,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-13T07:25:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04d3bb3cdc2d263f7e4056f16ef4728446c0720e","tid":2062420,"uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"r